<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/header.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/footer.css" />
    <title>About Us</title>
    <style>
        body{
            background-color: rgb(104, 164, 255);
        }
        .container {
            width: 80%;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }
        
        .container h2{
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .aboutcompany {
            background-color: white;
            width: 98%;
            border-radius: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            padding: 40px 60px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .aboutcompany img {
            position: absolute;
            top: 250px;
            right: 120px;
            width: 150px;
            height: auto;
        }

        .aboutteam {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .card {
            background-color: white;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            width: 310px;
            height: 250px;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 20px;
            position: relative;
            margin: 2%;
        }

        .card img {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            border-radius: 50%;
            width: 100px;
            height: 100px;
        }

        .info {
            margin-top: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .info h3 {
            margin-bottom: 10px
        }

        .info p {
            margin-bottom: 10px
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Header -->
    <%- include('../partials/header') %>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="aboutcompany">
            <img src="/images/default/favicon.png" alt="Company Logo">
            <h2>About Our Website</h2>
            <p>"Travel Together" is your one-stop shop for crafting extraordinary travel experiences. Our user-friendly website makes it simple to browse destinations, discover exciting tours and packages, and customize your itinerary to match your unique interests. Let us handle the logistics while you embark on an adventure filled with unforgettable moments. Whether you seek cultural immersion, thrilling outdoor activities, or luxurious relaxation, "Travel Together" helps you turn travel dreams into reality.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="aboutteam">
            <div class="card">
                <img src="/images/default/photo3.jpg">
                <div class="info">
                    <h3>ABHISHEK YADAV</h3>
                    <p>2115000040</p>
                    <b><p>FULLSTACK DEVELOPER</p></b>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
<script src="/js/userScript.js"></script>
<script src="/js/headerScript.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
